---
title: Hearty Beef, Bacon & Caramelised Onion Pie with Cheesy Potato Topping
description: You can have anything you want in a pie, it’s totally up to your tastebuds. May we suggest though, this beef version, it’s
homemade vibes are elevated when you add caramelised onion and bacon to the filling. If that’s not enough, there’s a real hit of
deliciousness by baking mashed potato on top to make the lid of the pie.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hearty-beef-pork-bacon-pie-a1092d7f.jpg
